# SyncCut UI Card Redesign Prompt

## Objective
Redesign the project cards to use a **modern SaaS feature-card style**.

The cards should feel **clean, modern, interactive, and premium**, similar to feature cards used in modern AI SaaS products and developer tools.

---

# Card Design

Each card should include:

- A **subtle dark gradient background** (dark gray with soft purple/teal gradient accents)
- **Rounded corners** (18px border radius)
- **Soft shadow for depth**
- A **faint border** separating the card from the background

Example styling:

background: #14141a  
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)  
box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)

---

# Visual Depth

Increase the **visual depth of the interface** so cards appear elevated above the page background.

Use a layered color structure:

| Layer | Color |
|------|------|
| Page Background | #0b0b0f |
| Card Surface | #14141a |
| Hover State | #1b1b23 |

This layered contrast prevents the UI from feeling flat and improves hierarchy.

---

# Card Content Layout

Inside the card:

### Top Left
A **small rounded-square icon container** with a light background.

### Title
A **bold title** representing the project name.

### Description
A **short description** in muted gray text.

---

# Spacing

Use generous spacing to keep the UI clean.

Recommended:

- **Padding:** 24–28px
- Comfortable vertical spacing between elements

Structure example:

Icon  

Title  

Description  

---

# Card Hover Interaction

Add micro-interactions when a user hovers over a card.

On hover:

- Card lifts slightly
- Shadow increases
- Border becomes slightly brighter
- Background becomes slightly lighter

Example animation:

transform: translateY(-4px)  
transition: all 0.2s ease

These hover interactions should feel **smooth and subtle**, similar to modern AI SaaS interfaces.

---

# Status Indicator Improvements

Replace plain status text with **visual status chips** so project states are instantly recognizable.

Statuses should appear as **pill-shaped badges**.

| Status | Color |
|------|------|
| Synced | Green |
| Processing | Blue |
| Exported | Purple |
| Draft | Gray |

Example chip styling:

padding: 4px 10px  
border-radius: 999px  
font-size: 12px  

Example color treatment:

background: rgba(0,255,150,0.1)  
border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,150,0.2)

This allows users to **quickly scan project states without reading text carefully**.

